This paper is primarily focused on knowledge transfer in deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed method to object detection, which is a computer vision task (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks for various applications, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of the Maximum Mean Discrepancy (MMD) metric, which is a common tool in the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
